    "Similarly, Yao et al (2023) leveraged BLEURT (Sellam et al 2020) and the deberta-v3-large-v2 reward model foot_6 to compare the generations for TruthfulQA (Lin et al 2022) questions by the original LLM with those resulting from unlearning harmful Q&A pairs of PKU-SafeRLHF (Ji et al 2023).",
    "-Same dataset but different samples.",
